### Enhanced nodes

* [AWS S3:](/integrations/builtin/app-nodes/n8n-nodes-base.awss3.md) Added Delete operation to the Bucket Resource.
* [Google Analytics:](/integrations/builtin/app-nodes/n8n-nodes-base.googleanalytics.md) Added Dimension Filters to the available Additional Fields.
* [HTTP Request:](/integrations/builtin/core-nodes/n8n-nodes-base.httprequest/index.md) Added Split Into Items option.
* [MQTT:](/integrations/builtin/app-nodes/n8n-nodes-base.mqtt.md) Added mqqts protocol for MQTT credentials.
* [QuickBooks:](/integrations/builtin/app-nodes/n8n-nodes-base.quickbooks.md) Added Purchase resource with Get and Get All operations.
